{"tid":1871740,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺自己有時好快寂寞，但有時又唔想再拍拖","createTime":"2020-02-09T16:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T05:14:30.000Z","uid":172031,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"09c250623317c66840ece33df80724a764732fc1","tid":1871740,"uid":172031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"如題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗自己唔係一個愛情玩家<br />\n我比較喜歡比一個我認為值得既人傾盡所有<br />\n<br />\n自從幾個月前分手後，有段時間個世界變佐灰白色；隨時日子一天一天咁過去，再潰爛既傷口都會埋口，只係有時會隱隱作痛。由攤係張床訓覺、到醉心電玩，然後投入工作；慢慢將自己變得愈來愈忙，試圖令大腦不能停止運轉。<br />\n<br />\n自從肺炎後，已經第二個星期冇翻工。每日除佐訓覺、炒股、打機、打J，就只係得翻思考。望住唔到既相片同日子，大腦又一下子陷入回憶既思緒。<br />\n<br />\n有時會想重新開始一段新感情<br />\n但有少少眉目既時候，有時又會寧願想自己一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知自己寫佐乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金牛座<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8wklbzYvXo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Di8wklbzYvXo&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqgqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=a1d3ac5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8wklbzYvXo</a><br />\n她的春秋，未必有我<br />\n我的春秋，卻留下刻骨銘心的故事"},{"pid":"b4686e25d9ec7131c579678136c7c7882f8145ec","tid":1871740,"uid":36403,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"習慣下就好 不過好快又會寂寞"},{"pid":"3705e1b3c9bc0ff468a55702ad8f37521fbede30","tid":1871740,"uid":232449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T16:08:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02db400c203cb1b97e4532eb545520c923a78ae6","tid":1871740,"uid":172031,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4686e25d9ec7131c579678136c7c7882f8145ec","tid":1871740